---
layout: base.vto
---

<div class="jumbotron container">
  <h1>Nostalgia Reimagined</h1>
  <p class="lead">Open source re-implementation of RollerCoaster Tycoon 3©.</p>
  <a href="play" class="btn call-to-action">Play Now</a>
</div>

<section id="features" class="features container">
  <h2 class="sr-only">Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li class="feature card">
      <h3>Enhanced Performance</h3>
      <p>Optimized for modern hardware and larger maps</p>
    </li>
    <li class="feature card">
      <h3>Cross Platform</h3>
      <p>Modern C# engine with web-based UI</p>
    </li>
    <li class="feature card">
      <h3>Full Gameplay</h3>
      <p>Base game including Soaked, & Wild expansions</p>
    </li>
    <li class="feature card">
      <h3>Community Extensions</h3>
      <p>Plugins for mods and enhancements</p>
    </li>
    <li class="feature card">
      <h3>UI Improvements</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Freeform, off-grid scenery placement</li>
        <li>Resizable Attractions, Structures, and Scenery windows</li>
        <li>etc.</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li class="feature card c2a">
      <h3 class="m-0">More Coming Soon</h3>
      <a class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary call-to-action" href="{{ wikiUrl }}/Roadmap">Roadmap</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="screenshots" class="container">
  <h2>Screenshots</h2>
  <figure>
    <img src="/screenshots/nullbmp.png" alt="Screenshot 1">
    <figcaption>Rendering the <c>nullbmp</c>.</figcaption>
  </figure>
  <!-- TODO: Add more screenshots -->
</section>

<section id="goals" class="features container">
  <h2>Future Goals</h2>
  <ul>
    <li class="feature card">
      <h3>Multiplayer</h3>
      <p>Online multiplayer with matchmaking and park-level security</p>
    </li>
    <li class="feature card">
      <h3>Independent Graphics</h3>
      <p>Eliminate the need for a copy of the game</p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="get-involved" class="container">
  <h2>Get Involved</h2>
  <p>
    Please feel free to share your ideas with us on the <a href="{{ forumUrl }}">forum</a> or on <a href="https://parkcrafters.com">ParkCrafters</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    Check out and comment on the <a href="{{ wikiUrl }}/Roadmap">Roadmap</a>, open <a href="https://github.com/open-rct3/open-rct3/discussions/new/choose">new discussion</a>, or <a href="https://github.com/sponsors/chances">buy us a coffee</a>.
    Every bit of your support helps us make this <abbr title="Some say pipe-dream...">dream</abbr> a reality!
  </p>
</section>
